{"tid":1594923,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[FC] 612基金係唔會資助買Gear及俾生活費！！！","createTime":"2019-09-25T20:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T19:41:45.000Z","uid":294440,"like":7,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2a0062fac0d6c1216a2e99fb42c0d4d1809cfe6a","tid":1594923,"uid":294440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係認真Post，希望大家留意番。感謝！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【 為免影響受傷、被捕的求助者，請勿再聯絡基金要求資助裝備 】</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n612人道支援基金得悉，有網上專頁呼籲市民向基金申請資助購買裝備及生活費。基金熱線於幾個小時內，已接獲近百個查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">＊＊＊基金重申，購買裝備或生活費並不是基金人道支援的範圍。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n希望大家明白，基金的角色是為反送中運動中的傷者或被捕者提供人道支援，而不是支援運動的抗爭基金。<br />\n<br />\n為免不必要的法律風險，並確保傷者/被捕者的醫療、法律、保釋金及緊急經濟援助等支援不受影響，基金必須謹慎行事。<br />\n<br />\n這些非必要的查詢，將影響真正有需要的朋友求助。基金呼籲有需要的傷者/被捕者如未收到回覆，請明日再次聯絡基金。不便之處，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n申請 ／ 查詢︰98456641 (Whatsapp / Telegram)<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 關於616遊行民陣音響，當日所有團體都為基金籌款並籌得1200萬。如果無音響係搞唔成遊行；如無遊行，612基金並不會籌到1200萬，所以音響的22萬是基金籌得1200萬的必要開支，基金因此決定支付是次遊行的音響費用。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/posts/419100045456832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2Fposts%2F419100045456832&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=2fa6f3c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/posts/419100045456832</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">另外，補充番612基金的動向 -</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n9月25日晚基金信託人許寶強、何韻詩直播：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/videos/370185667199473/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2Fvideos%2F370185667199473%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=66dfcf49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/videos/370185667199473/</a><br />\n基金現正支援9宗民事案件：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/photos/a.369803420386495/420156518684518/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2Fphotos%2Fa.369803420386495%2F420156518684518%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=7e6b29ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/photos/a.369803420386495/420156518684518/</a><br />\n基金工作簡報（截至9月20日）：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/photos/a.368493197184184/419554695411367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F612Fund%2Fphotos%2Fa.368493197184184%2F419554695411367%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=9a023522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/612Fund/photos/a.368493197184184/419554695411367/</a><br />\n基金工作簡報詳細數字，有幾個分頁的：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/612Fund_Report\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F612Fund_Report&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=575a90dd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/612Fund_Report</a>"},{"pid":"aa511a820a8d69ae844773a0f18539b4bf380e3a","tid":1594923,"uid":65847,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:44:39.000Z","msg":"收埋咁多錢要義士捱餓好撚人道呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01ca3329a1b92a662b880340499602a12797ebb","tid":1594923,"uid":147888,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:44:48.000Z","msg":"咁個7000幾萬不如撥去星火唔好?"},{"pid":"b45b6a118b55d6f31e57cc7c38a35b4c2e884ea8","tid":1594923,"uid":283335,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T20:57:22.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦612<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222a24b72848747fc00b2970a1